WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:11.669 --> 00:00:17.000
 Oh, this is really amazing, your fighting power increased to 40 thousand! 

00:00:18.150 --> 00:00:20.000
 It is true... 

00:00:20.519 --> 00:00:24.000
 You are totally different from the other Namekusei. 

00:00:25.980 --> 00:00:27.110
 You have left me... 

00:00:27.110 --> 00:00:29.600
 ... absolutely without words. 

00:00:30.069 --> 00:00:32.000
 You have great power. 

00:00:33.150 --> 00:00:35.100
 You are a true warrior. 

00:00:36.140 --> 00:00:44.700
 I would love for you to be part of my loyal group of soldiers, but as our great battle is about to begin ... 

00:00:45.200 --> 00:00:48.000
 ... I'll show you what my true fighting power is. 

00:00:48.000 --> 00:00:51.330
 My power ... is ... 

00:00:51.330 --> 00:00:53.190
 ... 53 thousand. 

00:00:53.190 --> 00:00:55.020
 But do not worry... 

00:00:55.020 --> 00:00:58.000
 ... because I'm not going to fight with all my strength. 

00:01:00.730 --> 00:01:02.070
 Already! 

00:01:02.070 --> 00:01:05.400
 I will fight only with my left hand! 

00:01:06.460 --> 00:01:09.300
 This may make it a little more fun. 

00:01:13.160 --> 00:01:18.000
 ENOUGH! ENOUGH! ENOUGH! ENOUGH! 

00:01:30.000 --> 00:01:32.000
 Go, go, go. 

00:01:32.470 --> 00:01:37.400
 And even though I put the collar on you so you would not fail, you could not do anything to me. 

00:01:38.090 --> 00:01:39.300
 But this... 

00:01:39.700 --> 00:01:43.300
 ... would be the best attack with a power of 42 thousand. 

00:02:00.880 --> 00:02:04.300
 Go, but what discourtesy mine. 

00:02:06.540 --> 00:02:07.700
 Hold your hand 

00:02:19.699 --> 00:02:23.300
 You should not take it so seriously, Nail. 

00:02:26.000 --> 00:02:33.000
 I think it's better that you confide the secret to me before I eliminate you. Do not you believe it? 

00:02:53.700 --> 00:02:56.200
 Oh, you surprised me! 

00:02:57.249 --> 00:03:01.600
 You can rebuild your hand, but even if you have it, the same thing will happen again. 

